      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused specimen featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six engine, equipped with individual throttle bodies and a 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise 6-speed manual transmission and a limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal torque distribution. This example has undergone critical preventative maintenance, including a professional rear subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul. The suspension geometry remains true, offering the telepathic turn-in these chassis are known for. Recent valve adjustments and rod bearing inspections confirm the mechanical integrity of the valvetrain and bottom end. A mechanically sound, visceral performer ready for the canyons.",
